%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 98b97d428ca44f1468506e98addd1ee8, type: 3}
  m_Name: Intro-HUE stops ONE
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 0}
  dialogue:
  - name: HUE
    portrait: {fileID: -758239331478521217, guid: ac16eba6361b6474eac13df7c5fa5dd1, type: 3}
    text: Stop right there. I'm to take that infected human to quarantine. Why do
      you continue to run away?
  - name: ONE
    portrait: {fileID: 1841309852453516274, guid: 867cea4d8e7ded24f8f219b7a85cdd28, type: 3}
    text: 'I won''t believe a single lie that comes out of your mouth! You don''t
      heal humans, you exterminate them. '
  - name: ONE
    portrait: {fileID: 1841309852453516274, guid: 867cea4d8e7ded24f8f219b7a85cdd28, type: 3}
    text: Eva... she won't last long without a cure. Just leave us be and I'm sure-
  - name: HUE
    portrait: {fileID: -758239331478521217, guid: ac16eba6361b6474eac13df7c5fa5dd1, type: 3}
    text: A cure? Even if you search the ends of the earth you won't find a cure.
  - name: HUE
    portrait: {fileID: -758239331478521217, guid: ac16eba6361b6474eac13df7c5fa5dd1, type: 3}
    text: You know her disease is highly infectious. How many more humans will you
      let her infect and kill before you accept reality?
  - name: HUE
    portrait: {fileID: -758239331478521217, guid: ac16eba6361b6474eac13df7c5fa5dd1, type: 3}
    text: Hand the human over, or else...
  responses: []
